original_client_text.markup_text:
If you think deeply, you’ll find a reason to give thanks always, especially for Jesus being our Mediator, our Saviour, and our Lord.
I know it might not look like it but you are very important to God….In spite of all that is happening…give thanks!

As you go about your week, may you find a reason to thank Him in Jesus’ name.

Have a fantastic week!
